            "id": 6260906,
            "title": "〈台股開盤〉台積電熄火 聯發科、鴻海撐盤不夠力 漲近百點後翻黑",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美股觀望聯準會降息，四大指數漲跌互現。台股今 (5) 日以 27796.43 點開出，上漲 0.72 點，台積電在平盤上下遊走，雖有聯發科上漲 30 元帶動廣達、鴻海等電子權值股走強，早盤一度漲近百點，但隨後指數隨台積電下跌翻黑。早盤估量 5072 億元。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6260906/l/85b8c9c4fe09883b41d5b388b2023a2d.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈台股開盤〉台積電熄火 聯發科、鴻海撐盤不夠力 漲近百點後翻黑。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>由於美國政府已停擺 43 天，陸續釋出的就業數據皆為非官方的次級報告，對於勞動市場的評估有高度不確定性，然而市場仍看好聯準會於本月降息 1 碼，並於 2026 年啟動降息循環。而台股在基本面穩定下，整體仍呈觀望情緒。</p></section><section>\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>電子權值股漲多於跌，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 持平，來到 1445 元；聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 上漲 25 元，漲近 2%；廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 、鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 漲近 1%，日月光投控 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>)、台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 均於平盤下方 。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>伺服器類股走強，緯穎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6669:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6669\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6669-TW</a>)、緯創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3231:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3231\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3231-TW</a>) 漲逾 3%，英業達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2356:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2356\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2356-TW</a>) 漲逾 2%，永擎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7711-TW</a>) 漲逾 1%，華碩 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2357:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2357\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2357-TW</a>) 漲近 1%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p> </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
